(32, 'INSIGHT - Edisi 6', '2019-11-10', 'https://webdev.rifhandi.com/uploads/filesupload/sample.pdf', '<p>INSIGHT edisi keenam&nbsp;: Industri Halal Indonesia</p>\r\n\r\n<p>INSIGHT merupakan media&nbsp;informasi yang menyajikan analisis perkembangan kondisi ekonomi dan keuangan syariah serta pemikiran tokoh ekonomi syariah Indonesia. INSIGHT diterbitkan KNKS setiap bulan&nbsp;dalam rangka meningkatkan edukasi dan literasi masyarakat mengenai ekonomi dan keuangan syariah.</p>', 1, '2019-11-10 15:18:16', '2019-11-11 15:28:36', NULL, 7, 'INSIGHT - 6th Edition', '<p>INSIGHT 6th edition : Indonesia Halal Industry</p>\r\n\r\n<p>INSIGHT is a platform that contains analysis of Indonesian Islamic economic development and thoughts of the Islamic economic experts. It is monthly bulletin that aims to improve people literacy on Islamic economy. This 6th&nbsp;edition talks about Indonesia&#39;s Halal Industry.</p>', 'kneks'),
